      <abstract>
        <p>Testimony of K.E. (1908) and G.F. [Fanny Grünzberger] (1911) on the Kamenets-Podolsk
          deportations in 1941, ghettoization in Ungvár/Uzhorod and deportation to Auschwitz in May,
          1944, and their sufferings in the Bergen-Belsen and Salzwedel labour camps.</p>
      </abstract>
